Serial2web
---------

[About]
Simple applicatiom to transfrom serialinput from Current Cost to webrequests. Very useful when pushing data from any serial device to data infrastructures like Pachube or AMEE. To used with Arduino+Ethernet boards.

[How to Use]
Change rxPin to the to the pin connected to Current Cost
Change byte server[] = {xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx } to the hostname your are posting to
Change client.println("Host: hostname"); to the hostname your are posting to

[Requires]
<SPI.h>
<Ethernet.h>
<NewSoftSerial.h>
<string.h>
<stdio.h>